criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Young patients with exacerbation of autoimmune disease, requiring 1-2mg/kg/day
             prednisone or equivalent for treatment;

          -  could undergo <15mg/kg/day prednisone or equivalent glucocorticoid maintenance in the
             previous three months;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with history of diabetes;

          -  patients with severe organ dysfunction or failure;

          -  patients with febrile conditions;
